metadata.name: FunTotem #1
metadata.description:
FunTotems NFTs is a limited collection of beautiful, funny, bewitching, mischievous animal art!

Artworks is created and completely hand-drawn by @pink_dust ART.

By owning FunTotems you become a lifetime member of the pink_dust ART Club and are on our whitelist, they give you the opportunity to have privileges on the giveaway and when minting our NFTs.
